{"tid":8252,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"夏薩特😎：只有兩隊能與車路士爭英超冠軍😡❗️❗️","createTime":"2016-11-28T08:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T09:40:09.000Z","uid":20611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc4d50533b8709b0d5397a157f1cc0d44bafad3f","tid":8252,"uid":20611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:51:36.000Z","msg":"【三分天下】夏薩特：只有兩隊能與車路士爭英超冠軍！<br />\n<br />\n目前，車路士在13輪英超賽事完結後，以1分的優勢，繼續領先聯賽榜，而他們下一仗的對手將是豪強曼城。<br />\n<br />\n在接受訪問時，夏薩特表示如今只有兩支球隊，能夠為車路士的爭冠帶來威脅，他們分別是利物浦和曼城。夏薩特說：「利物浦和曼城均很出色，如果車路士希望笑到最後，必先想方法超越他倆。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們下一仗將對陣曼城，而他們陣中擁有許多出色的球員，例如阿古路和奇雲迪布尼。奇雲迪布尼曾於車路士遇上低潮，<span style=\"color: red;\">但這只是教練的戰術不符球員的風格而已</span>😝，但他還是一位十分自信的球員，希望他在倒戈藍軍時不要那麼自信吧，哈哈！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://football.fanpiece.com/m/soccerfunnymoment/c1255654.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fsoccerfunnymoment%2Fc1255654.html&d=icry47PlOih8PFT35jB9t8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=98acae20\" target=\"_blank\">http://football.fanpiece.com/m/soccerfunnymoment/c1255654.html</a>"},{"pid":"4f7dc013d85044bfa0336e570aea9978bb7102b1","tid":8252,"uid":10897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:53:01.000Z","msg":"冇阿狗份，sick ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb79f90ea27ae8ff4d5ff703ab7c4f668bc8f0f","tid":8252,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:53:08.000Z","msg":"Daddy 又比人抽水"},{"pid":"beff40430fd693247226f8cbbec2dc0411cd4873","tid":8252,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"出賣daddy嘅反骨仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a880fe482d8159448098abfb34da6557b15ad75","tid":8252,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"世三反哥的確可取<br />\n但反雲就顯得智力有問題"},{"pid":"f3782a8d3a25eed0b1fcf5ce24cd5f599512c6b6","tid":8252,"uid":1838